You need GNU Make:

    http://www.gnu.org/software/make/

You also need the tsocks library:

    http://tsocks.sourceforge.net/

In the future, it may be possible to use the Torsocks library:

    http://code.google.com/p/torsocks/

If you'd like to make a Debian binary package:

    make deb

If you'd like to make a Debian source package:

    make deb-src
